title: Saying Goodbye To YouTube
description: On this episode of H3 Off The Rails Ethan reaffirms his commitment to the YouTube platform FOREVER. Ethan and the team discuss Joe Rogan's big mommy milkers, try Popeye's unforgettable chicken nuggies, give some more unpopular opinions, Dan refuses to stand up, and a whole lot more!
